## Why No EPF Issue?

**Common Situations:**
- Self-employed (no EPF)
- Business owner (EPF optional)
- Foreigner (no EPF)
- Small business (not contributing)
- **Banks require EPF proof**

## 2026 No EPF Solutions

**Income-Based Approval:**

**Instead of EPF, We Accept:**
- Business bank statements
- SOCSO contributions
- Business tax returns
- Business revenue proof
- **Income verified via business**

