## No EPF vs Bank Requirements

| Requirement | Bank | Income-Based Solution |
|-------------|-------|----------------------|
| **EPF** | Required | Not required |
| **Proof** | EPF statement | Bank statements, tax |
| **Approval** | Auto-reject no EPF | Income-based approval |
| **Rate** | Same | Same |

## Documentation (No EPF)

**Acceptable Proof:**

1. **Business Bank Statements**
   - 6-12 months
   - Regular deposits
   - Business income
   - **Primary proof**

2. **Business Tax Returns**
   - Latest Form B
   - Business income declared
   - Tax paid
   - **Supporting proof**

3. **SOCSO** (if any)
   - Contributions made
   - Employee records
   - **Helpful**

